# 6001CEM Project - Student Dashboard Prototype

## Project Overview
This repository contains a **prototype** for the **6001CEM Individual Project** by **Taha Amir Khan** (Student ID: **11651879**). The project is designed as a **Student Dashboard** for Coventry University, integrating interactive UI elements, notifications, and a timetable.

## Repository Contents
- `index.html` - Main HTML structure for the student dashboard
- `styles.css` - CSS styles for layout and UI design
- `script.js` - JavaScript for interactive elements and modals
- `coventry-logo.png` - Coventry University logo used in the header
- `aula-logo.jpeg` - Aula logo used in the coursework section

## Features
- **Student Dashboard Interface**: Provides a centralized student portal experience.
- **Interactive Notifications**: Displays alerts for coursework deadlines, exam registration, and more.
- **Timetable Integration**: Weekly schedule layout for student classes.
- **Document Requests**: Ability to generate student-related documents.
- **Grade Overview**: Displays recent grades and overall academic progress.

## Deployment
This prototype is hosted via **GitHub Pages** for demonstration purposes. Ensure that all assets are correctly linked when hosting locally or deploying to a different environment.

## Usage Instructions
1. Clone the repository:
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/your-github-username/repository-name.git
   ```
2. Open `index.html` in a browser to view the prototype.
3. Modify `styles.css` or `script.js` as needed to customize the dashboard functionality.

## Future Improvements
- Implement backend integration for real-time student data retrieval.
- Enhance UI/UX for better accessibility and responsiveness.
- Expand notification features to include real-time push updates.

